Artwork was superb and sex scenes were excellent! Fap worthy every page, but the niece truly is just one of the most unlikeable characters ever, she was just always aggressively pushing on her aunt to get her to be with her, but at no point does she ever consider her feelings. I know we see her be somewhat redeemed when it shows she did not sleep with her ex, thus showing her love for her aunt Masumi only was true, but she never displayed much love to her in the sense of consideration of her feelings until the last few pages, she was just honestly to me, just another horny teen without any depth of character and I could see her choosing to go out with the ex, even though she was reluctant, due to the fact she looked like her aunt. It also took too long for the Aunt to be more assertive in the sex scenes just to later submit to her niece. But again, art was phenomenal! Really hope to see more from the author!
